2. fakebook PROFILE NAME Logout Jacqueline Kennedy Oh my goodness that was such a close race between Jack and Richard Nixon! Thank goodness we won. November 8th, 1960 Jacqueline Kennedy Today is the day that me and Jack will be married! We’re getting married at St. Mary’s church in Newport, Rhode Island. September 12, 1953 Jacqueline Kennedy Today I met a guy named John Kennedy also known as Jack I I like him thanks to one friends Charles L Bartlett…. May 1952 Jacqueline Kennedy I arrived in Paris! Cant wait to start at the University of Grenoble in Grenoble. 1949 Jacqueline Kennedy Today is my first day in college at Vassar College in Poughkeepsie, New York! 1947 Jacqueline Kennedy I graduate from Miss Porter’s boarding school today! Eeek! I am super excited! Soon I will no longer be Connecticut! June 1947 Jacqueline Kennedy Today Mom is marrying Hugh Auchincloss he is a business man and has 3 kids I guess he is okay. 1942
